nfirmation email. Once the confirmation email has been received, students may obtain a", "bracelet by visiting SHS during office hours in their new office located in The Beekley Center", "for Student Health and Wellness on the first floor of the O\u2019Connell Athletic Center. Office hours", "\u2013 \u2013 are Monday Friday, 8:30 a.m. 4:30 p.m., and masks are required for entry. Bracelets will also", "be available during special hours on campus move in days.", "Students who are confirmed as fully vaccinated will no longer have to complete the Daily", "Attestation form when utilizing USJ Wi-Fi. If they are identified as a close contact to someone", "who tests positive, but they are not symptomatic themselves, they will not be required to", "quarantine or be tested.", "When on campus, employees and students wearing this bracelet will not be required to wear", "masks indoors except to enter the Gengras Center, the School for Young Children, and Student", "Health Services. Employees and students who are not wearing this bracelet must continue", "wearing masks at all times while indoors on campus, unless alone in a private office, and must", "wear a mask outdoors when in the vicinity of the Gengras Center or School for Young Children.", "Students in lab or clinical courses may be asked to wear a mask, regardless of vaccination status,", "based upon curricular requirements.", "Students with questions or who are experiencing difficulties submitting the form should contact", "Student Health Services at 860.231.5530 or healthservices@usj.edu."], "bbox": [[0.117688, 0.192894, 0.67408, 0.020985], [0.117688, 0.22748, 0.719255, 0.020212], [0.117688, 0.244879, 0.758952, 0.020212], [0.117688, 0.262556, 0.759106, 0.020212], [0.117688, 0.279917, 0.6737839999999999, 0.020212], [0.117688, 0.297278, 0.746089, 0.020212], [0.117688, 0.314639, 0.741293, 0.020212], [0.117688, 0.331987, 0.7242109999999999, 0.020212], [0.117688, 0.349702, 0.7386079999999999, 0.020212], [0.117688, 0.367063, 0